{"tid":748572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"按鐘冇人落車　九巴車長疑與乘客爆衝突","createTime":"2018-07-19T10:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T10:57:48.000Z","uid":75969,"like":145,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9d37d7913dcf55c9bdb79f06159694e3b77366","tid":748572,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/photo/bkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180719175707\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180719175707&h=8b1ebe14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">疑按鐘冇人落車，引發車長遇襲事件。(讀者提供)</span><br />\n<br />\n九巴車長疑不滿有乘按鐘後無人落車，與乘客爆發衝突。今晨（19日）6時許，一輛由藍田往葵涌的38號路線九巴，載客途經荔枝角青山公路鍾山臺時，有乘客按了落車鐘，車長於是埋站，將落車門打開，但發覺車上沒有乘客要落車，疑引起車長不滿，據目擊事件經過的其中一名乘客廖先生表示，當時車長沒有即時閂門開車，等了近兩分鐘，車長查問:「有冇人落車。」<br />\n<br />\n廖稱，他好心向車長表示:「可能有人按錯鐘，好小事啫!」其他乘客亦開口說:「唔好嘈啦，趕返工，開番車啦!」一眾乘客開始鼓譟。據悉，期間上層一名年約35歲的男乘客憤然走落下層，揮拳毆打車長後逃去，車長於報警，姓王(33歲)車長報稱額頭受傷，由救護員送院治療。事件擾攘約10分鐘，隨後的2班車都已抵達該站，車上乘客轉乘另一班車，警方將案件列作襲擊，將對案件作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/photo/bkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180719175707\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180719175707&h=d300173c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其他乘客落車轉乘另一輛巴士離開。(讀者提供)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/photo/bkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180719175707\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180719175707&h=5225721b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">報稱遇襲的車長。(讀者提供)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/bkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180719%2Fbkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001.html&d=ZLe4iOmHm5XT7L3rTUyYzU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=bd4390a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180719/bkn-20180719162325915-0719_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c7aacd3bc88414722b2cec3fb2661ee62b685e9","tid":748572,"uid":181819,"like":53,"dislike":200,"score":-147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"個司機咁屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ab191b654342ff746ff075ea17f74b97dea3df","tid":748572,"uid":36441,"like":307,"dislike":28,"score":279,"quote":{"pid":"3c7aacd3bc88414722b2cec3fb2661ee62b685e9","tid":748572,"uid":181819,"like":53,"dislike":200,"score":-147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"個司機咁屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:15:16.000Z","msg":"比人打都屎忽鬼？"},{"pid":"5d577433eda0fa59875a3e7203c4ee91f608ab58","tid":748572,"uid":29764,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個司機咁屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>比人打都屎忽鬼？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"aa5afab348faf24909630856876054745534499d","tid":748572,"uid":85556,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:15:47.000Z","msg":"保持兩秒距離好d"},{"pid":"cae5ee6a398245c3c4cd961005e07f94e443bd80","tid":748572,"uid":6783,"like":240,"dislike":18,"score":222,"quote":{"pid":"3c7aacd3bc88414722b2cec3fb2661ee62b685e9","tid":748572,"uid":181819,"like":53,"dislike":200,"score":-147,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"個司機咁屎忽鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"咁又屎忽 <br />\n如果真係有客要落 佢又開車走左咁點